    "Edited Writeup": "Mike Curry Mike lives in Sisters, Oregon. His kids are doing well; he has no grandchildren yet. He's been sober for decades and looks for activities that don't involve alcohol. His plebe company was F4, graduating from C2. He loved the pranks cadets used to play, like putting a boat in the messhall for Army-Navy. He served in Germany, which he found wonderful, then attended grad school in Oregon, which really shaped his after-Army life. He's now a professor at Oregon State working virtually. He's single and pretty active, doing a lot of acrobatics and rock climbing. He can be reached at michael@webmentors.com | 541-408-1693."
