    "Edited Writeup": "Jud Hoff Jud lives in Hilton Head Island, South Carolina. He has four children: a married daughter with two kids in Michigan; a son (USMA 2014) who is married with two kids in Chicago; an engaged son in North Carolina; and a daughter in grad school in South Carolina. His plebe company was B3, graduating from C2. He completed Flight School (UH60) and served at Fort Lewis with 2-9 Aviation, Honduras, and fighting forest fires in Yellowstone. After the Army, he spent 26 years with Stryker Corporation in various division and corporate leadership roles, retiring in 2016. Since retirement he started two nonprofits, serves as angel investor for seven entities (leading two), and holds multiple board positions for nonprofits and for-profits. He's an avid pickleball player and weightlifter, a consummate researcher about health, fitness, and cancer treatment who has developed protocols for cancer treatment, and is developing expertise in blockchain quantum security. He enjoys sporting events and rock concerts. He can be reached at judhoff123@yahoo.com | 269-207-1268."
