    "Metro Area": "Omaha",
    "Edited Writeup": "Pete and his wife, Shelly, live in Papillion, Nebraska.  They have two daughters, both live in Omaha, NE; Lyndsie is a nurse anesthetist and Lorrin is an Early Childhood/Special Education Teacher.  Pete and Shelly have been blessed with three grandsons. Pete served in Hanau, Germany before returning to Fort Sill as a Gunnery Instructor and commanding a Battery before going to NSA to work in his Functional Area.  Pete left the Army and began working at the National Security Agency in Information Assurance.  He PCS’d from NSA HQ to the U.S. Strategic Command in 2001 and has been there since.  Pete retired from government service in June 2026 and spends his time golfing, fishing, and smoking meats, and he can still beat Craig Doescher in racquetball with little effort.  Pete can be reached at pjlafleur@icloud.com | 402-659-2527."
