    "Edited Writeup": "David Pinder Dave lives in Eden Prairie, Minnesota. He and his wife just had their first two grandchildren on September 1, 2025, twins, a boy and a girl. His plebe company was E2, graduating from C3. He served 10 years on active duty, including as a Desert Storm battery commander and later as a West Point TAC for Company G-4. His cadet memories are all positive—\"not one bad memory\" and he considers it an honor to be a member of the class. After the Army, he's been in the glass business for 28 years, serving the last 14 years as President of Cardinal Insulating Glass. Roughly 70% of all residential windows and doors contain Cardinal glass. He enjoys golf, sporting events, and \"anything really.\" He can be reached at dpinder@cardinalcorp.com | 952-240-4816."
