    "Plebe Co": "A2",
    "Town": "Grand Rapids",
    "State": "MI",
    "Edited Writeup": "Stephen Steffes Steve  lives in Grand Rapids, Michigan on the farm where he grew up, they literally \"bought the farm.\" He and his wife Theresa have four children (three boys and a girl) and five grandchildren.  He served at Fort Hood as well as at Aschaffenburg and Schweinfurt, Germany. He particularly appreciates those assignments where he got to meet and enjoy time with so many good people.  He really learned to appreciate the sacrifices of classmates and their families who served extended periods of time in Iraq and Afghanistan after his own short deployment under much better conditions during the First Gulf War. His favorite cadet memories are visits from Theresa and hanging out with classmates. After the Army, he pursued a career in operations management in the pharmaceutical industry. The events around COVID while he and Theresa were working out of Dublin were probably the most interesting, though not the most pleasant. He enjoys travel, service events, and sports events. He can be reached at sjsteffes86@gmail.com | 616-450-1676."
