    "Edited Writeup": "Kathie Stewart-Kelley KASK lives in Southern Pines, North Carolina. Her roomies are her mum, Pat, and Tuppence, a crazy mutt. Her son is using his GI Bill toward a degree in biology and environmental science at UMass Boston. She deployed to Desert Storm with the 89th MPs out of Fort Hood. After the Army, she spent two years in retail management, six years as a Dallas Police officer, and 26 years and counting at Travelers Insurance Company. She hikes, knits, enjoys historical tours, and wine and spirits tasting. She is always reading at least four books at once and loves to discuss them with everyone and anyone. Apparently two book clubs are not enough. Her dream retirement job is already waiting for her at the local independent book shop. She can be reached at kask6993@gmail.com | 860-329-3445."
