    "Edited Writeup": "Antonio Williams Antonio lives in Houston, Texas. He has been married to Arlene for over 37 years. They have two daughters: Katherine lives in Las Vegas and Elizabeth lives in Louisville, Kentucky. His plebe company was I1, graduating from E4. His most memorable cadet experiences were Glee Club participation, including performing at an NBA All Star game, and playing on the Handball Team at the Pentagon against Army officers stationed there. He served at Fort Knox for OBC, then Fort Polk for his first assignment as platoon leader, XO, battalion staff, and brigade staff. He returned to Knox, then did one year in Korea on brigade staff in 2nd Infantry Division, then back to Polk where he left the Army in 1992. After leaving the Army in 1992, he went into the chemicals business, ran a sales team for Honeywell, ran a plant for Amcor Flexibles, and currently runs a business that produces polymeric resin binder in rocket propellant for solid rocket motors used in aerospace and defense systems. He plays racquetball a few times a week when not traveling for business. He and Arlene frequently cruise out of Galveston, Texas whenever they can. He enjoys attending games, golf, and travel. He can be reached at arlenegwilliams@aol.com | 281-435-5447."
